 {"id":"bd-mblr.5.5.2","title":"Retrofit all e2e scripts to unified detailed logging schema","description":"Update each e2e integration script to emit structured, schema-compliant logs at key lifecycle boundaries (start, setup, execute, validate, artifact bundle, terminal status). Acceptance: no script emits ad-hoc-only terminal messages; all script outputs include traceable event records with artifact pointers and failure context.","design":"Migrate by script family with reusable logging helpers and contract checks to avoid one-off formatting divergence.","acceptance_criteria":"1. Every e2e script emits schema-compliant structured events for lifecycle boundaries: start, setup, execute, validate, artifact-bundle, terminal. 2. Required traceability fields (trace/run/scenario/seed/outcome/duration/error/artifact refs) are always present. 3. No required script remains ad-hoc-terminal-output-only for diagnostics.","notes":"Retrofit sequencing depends on inventory + unified schema migration so script outputs remain interoperable with existing tooling.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:29:27.569786055Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:47:08.251957791Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.5.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.4.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:46:39.815805148Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.5.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.5.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:29:27.569786055Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.5.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.3.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:29:27.569786055Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.5.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.5","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:29:27.569786055Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_